  "body": "Nowadays it is needed to restart the desktop application to apply new language setting on Linux OS. A popup is shown to ask the user to quit the app. \r\n\r\nHere the current popup behaviour:\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97019400/161928461-3e0977e8-108f-4e1c-9d6a-d4ba6c2c8153.mp4\r\n\r\nThe expected behaviour is the same than on the other OS, so **the language should follow an 'auto-save' pattern.**\r\n\r\nRelated to [PR #5300](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/5300)",
